Direct Known Subclasses:
And, Or, TransitiveAnd
public abstract class CompoundMatcher
extends AbstractMatcher

Abstract class supporting compound matchers. All constituent sub-matchers must use the same annotation and antecedent types, otherwise a ResourceInstantiationException will be raised.
